hống lao và suyễn.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li><li style="margin-bottom: 3px; text-align: justify; user-select: auto;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; user-select: auto;"><span style="background: white; user-select: auto;"><span style="line-height: normal; user-select: auto;"><span style="user-select: auto;"><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; user-select: auto;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; user-select: auto;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; user-select: auto;"><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); user-select: auto;">Nâng đỡ hệ thống tiêu hóa, tiêu chảy và táo bón.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li><li style="margin-bottom: 3px; text-align: justify; user-select: auto;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; user-select: auto;"><span style="background: white; user-select: auto;"><span style="line-height: normal; user-select: auto;"><span style="user-select: auto;"><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; user-select: auto;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; user-select: auto;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; user-select: auto;"><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); user-select: auto;">Giải độc, ngăn ngừa kích ứng da, viêm da và các bệnh về da.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li></ul>',
